race.comment: MR. PRESIDENT (5) was a last start winner this course and distance taking a Grade 5 in 29.10 in one of the quickest times on the card and clocking a personal best as well. Can measure up again if runs up to latest. STEELE JAKIT (2) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at Warragul over 460m behind Mia Neo (26.68) in a Grade 5. Form from his last run is proving strong. One of the main contenders. EXCAVATOR TICKET (1) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at Sandown over 715m behind Greysynd Sammy (43.12) in a Grade 4/5. Key runner on best form. BROCKY SANDS (6) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to atone. Something for the Multiples: MR. PRESIDENT (5)
